additional_attributes:
application=

Withabms Safe-Green? 2X PCR Taq MasterMix, you can
Reduce PCR set up time
Eliminate ethidium bromide usage and associated waste disposal costs
Increase PCR efficiency and reproducibility

The use ofTaq DNA Polymerasein this MasterMix offers:
Robust PCR performance with great reproducibility
High sensitivity

,cart2quote_quotable=Use default,format_general=5 x 1ml vials,hot_start=No,inert_dye=With SafeGreen Dye,internal_leadtime=---,invisible_search_keywords=Taq DNA Polymerase bundle, cobra,note=

It is strongly recommended to use the following DNA markers to analyze the PCR product:
Safe-Green? 100bp Opti-DNA Marker(Cat. G473)
Safe-Green? 1kb Opti-DNA Marker(Cat. G474)

Safe-Green? Excitation: max= 495 nm
Safe-Green? Emission: max= 520 nm


This product is ISO-13485 certified.

,polymerase_format=MasterMix- with Dye,product_quote=No,reactions=200,storage_condition=
